name: THE JUDGE'S GAZE
description:
Our researcher was able to access the room where a gigantic entity lived, the scale of which exceeded any form of life on earth.

After taking several photographs with his mobile to collect evidence of what he was experiencing, he fell as a result of a dematerialization of the entire scene.

We are still waiting for news of his whereabouts.

Art and Animation by Flores Solano.
2021
Muse: Sofía Rangel Blanco.
